{"tid":2297819,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「回港易」截至6時共2140人經計劃入境","createTime":"2020-11-23T14:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T16:44:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1919f5501778d0e69b19df5a1f909865e4cfc3bf","tid":2297819,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561501-20201123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561501-20201123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUncljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=6ee21bfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561501-20201123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a46069cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561501-20201123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府推出的「回港易計劃」，截至下午6時，有2140人經計劃返港，約1810人使用深圳灣口岸，約330人使用港珠澳大橋香港口岸。這些香港居民由廣東省或澳門回港後可獲豁免檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n政府說，為加快通關流程，減少輪候時間，以及避免在口岸出現網絡連接問題，強烈呼籲計劃經回港易計劃入境的香港居民，除了緊記須在預約的指定日期及口岸回港外，也應在出發回港前的24小時內，透過「粵康碼」或「澳康碼」轉碼至衞生署的電子健康申報表系統，以取得綠色二維碼，入境香港後可獲豁免強制檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n當局指，如「轉碼」後取得其他顏色的二維碼，例如粉紅色，代表未能符合所有指明條件，回港可能須接受14天強制檢疫。"},{"pid":"2a4a10be2baddd1b6d021c0f7f2e4ffec17f6bd3","tid":2297819,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"派5000 點都番黎拎<br />\n免費14日住宿+5000大洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲正過staycation <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64fb41f1c98b077f7c81c80a9380f1280594e17","tid":2297819,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T14:36:56.000Z","msg":"仆你個街又開一個窿放毒入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106acd7c659a469edf63aff9e605476b40678b62","tid":2297819,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T14:37:45